## Limitations
The findings are based on available literature and may not encompass all aspects of the psychological motivations behind reading negative comments. The data is also limited to studies and articles available up to October 2023, and newer research may provide additional insights. Furthermore, individual differences in psychological makeup mean that not all findings will apply universally.